sequenceDiagram
  participant Agent
  participant Tools as MCP tools
  participant Service as Rust service
  participant Backend as Native backend
  participant UI as Real UI

  Agent->>Tools: Discover capabilities
  Tools->>Service: Request backend readiness
  Service->>Backend: Probe capture input accessibility
  Backend-->>Service: Ready partial or blocked
  Service-->>Agent: Capability report
  Agent->>Tools: Inspect screen or tree
  Tools->>Service: Capture current state
  Service->>UI: Screenshot or UI query
  UI-->>Service: Current evidence
  Service-->>Agent: Observable state
  Agent->>Tools: Act with semantic or coordinate input
  Tools->>Service: Execute checked action
  Service->>Backend: Native input
  Backend-->>Agent: Result or precise failure
